defaultDCLG, BIS, the Cabinet Office and the Local Government Association have been working together to look at what more councils can do to get best value from their procurement of construction projects.  The government’s industrial strategy for construction was launched on 2nd July
default and sets out how we can work with the construction industry to ensure the 
defaultUK
